# Prismatic · Environment Variables Reference

## Required

### LLM Provider
```
# Choose provider: deepseek (default, cost-effective), openai, or anthropic
LLM_PROVIDER=deepseek

# DeepSeek API (recommended — $0.14/1M tokens input)
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-your-key

# OR OpenAI API
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-key

# OR Anthropic API
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key
```

## Optional

### Authentication (NextAuth.js)
```
# Required: Generate with `openssl rand -base64 32`
AUTH_SECRET=your-secret-key-here

# GitHub OAuth App
# Create at: https://github.com/settings/developers
AUTH_GITHUB_ID=your-github-client-id
AUTH_GITHUB_SECRET=your-github-client-secret

# Google OAuth App
# Create at: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
AUTH_GOOGLE_ID=your-google-client-id
AUTH_GOOGLE_SECRET=your-google-client-secret

# Optional: NextAuth URL (defaults to NEXTAUTH_URL for compatibility)
NEXTAUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=your-secret-key-here  # Legacy variable name
```

### Analytics
```
NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY=phc_your_key
```

### Storage
```
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=
S3_BUCKET=prismatic-archives
AWS_REGION=us-east-1
```

## Model Configuration

| Provider | Model | Input $/1M | Output $/1M | Recommended For |
|----------|-------|-----------|-------------|----------------|
| DeepSeek | deepseek-chat | $0.14 | $0.28 | Default — best value |
| DeepSeek | deepseek-reasoner | $0.59 | $1.85 | Complex reasoning |
| OpenAI | gpt-4o | $2.50 | $10.00 | Premium quality |
| OpenAI | gpt-4o-mini | $0.15 | $0.60 | Budget option |
| Anthropic | claude-sonnet-4 | $3.00 | $15.00 | Long context |
